data.description: With 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a 1-car attached garage, this property provides ample space for comfortable living. As you step inside, you'll notice the new flooring throughout the main living area and the newer paint throughout. The new closet systems provide convenient storage solutions for your belongings. The spacious fenced yard is perfect for outdoor activities. Additionally, the back covered screened deck provides a peaceful spot to relax and enjoy the outdoors. The walkout basement allows access to the attached garage, has a full finished bathroom, and plenty of storage space. This house benefits from its proximity to various amenities such as shops, restaurants, and parks. Commuting is made easy with access to major highways nearby. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your new home!
